<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">你昨晚睡得好吗？<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这座<tag a="110" b="32" /><delay20 />一到夜里就会变得超级安静呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />正因如此，让人能舒服地一觉睡到大天亮！<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，<delay8 />我倒是觉得，
再热闹一点也不错！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />搬来<tag a="110" b="32" />上的第一天，<delay20 />一直忙着整理行李，<delay8 />
可把我累坏了！<pageBreak /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一想到，<delay8 />
终于要开始新的生活了，<delay20 />
就忍不住<delay8 />兴奋起来！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />谢谢你<delay8 />那么关心我！<delay frames="30" />
